==Introduction==
陸軍で開発、対潜哨戒機としても運用されていた固定翼機です。<br>
現代のSTOL(短距離離着陸機)のような性能を持ち、艦載対潜哨戒機として運用されました。<br>
全通甲板を持つ強襲揚陸艦や軽空母などで運用可能です。

''The Type 3 Liaison fixed-wing aircraft (Kokusai Ki-76) was a military project developed for anti-submarine operations. Similar to the STOL (Short Take-off and Landing) aircraft of today, this aircraft is carried aboard warships as an anti-submarine aircraft. It can use the flight decks of a landing ship or a light aircraft carrier.''

==Notes==
CVL equipped with this plane will still require a dive bomber (red) or a torpedo bomber (blue) to attack SS, as they are unable to attack anything without a bomber.

